div(ng-show='vm.page.action.isTraining')
  p.question.p-required Is the email you've provided your 
    strong work 
    | email address?
  md-input-container.md-block(flex)
    md-radio-group(ng-model='vm.section.emailIsWork', name='emailIsWork', required)
      md-radio-button(value='yes', ng-click='vm.changeEmailWork()') Yes
      md-radio-button(value='no', ng-click='vm.changeEmailWork()')  No
    div(ng-messages='vm.form.emailIsWork.$error')
      div(ng-message='required')
        | This field is required
  md-input-container.md-block(flex, ng-hide="vm.section.emailIsWork === 'yes'")
    label What is your  
      strong work 
      | email address?
    input(
      required,
      type='email',
      name='contactWorkEmail',
      ng-model='vm.page.contact.npe01__WorkEmail__c',
      minlength='10',
      maxlength='155',
      ng-pattern="/^.+@.+\..+$/"
    )
    div(ng-messages='vm.form.contactWorkEmail.$error')
      div(ng-message-exp="['minlength', 'maxlength', 'pattern']")
        | Your email must be between 10 and 155 characters long and look like an e-mail address.
div(ng-hide='vm.page.action.isTraining')
  p.question.p-required Would you like your email added to the APF mailing list?
  md-input-container.md-block(flex)
    md-radio-group(ng-model='vm.page.contact.AddEmailToMailingList', name='contactEmailOptOut', required)
      md-radio-button(value='1') Yes
      md-radio-button(value='0') No
    div(ng-messages='vm.form.contactEmailOptOut.$error')
      div(ng-message='required')
        | This field is required
md-input-container.md-block(flex)
  label Phone 
  input(ng-model='vm.section.phoneNumber', name='contactPhone', required)
  div(ng-messages='vm.form.contactPhone.$error')
    div(ng-message='required')
      | This field is required
md-input-container.md-block(flex)
  label Which phone number is this?
  md-select(ng-model='vm.page.contact.npe01__PreferredPhone__c', name='contactPreferredPhone', required)
    md-option(ng-repeat='phoneType in vm.section.phoneTypes', value='{{ phoneType }}')
      | {{ phoneType }}
  //- div.hint
  //-   | Is it you work phone, mobile phone, home phone?
  div(ng-messages='vm.form.contactPreferredPhone.$error')
    div(ng-message='required')
      | This field is required
md-input-container.md-block(flex)
  label Fax 
  input(ng-model='vm.page.contact.Fax', name='contactFax')
  //- div(ng-messages='vm.form.contactFax.$error')
  //-   div(ng-message='required')
  //-     | This field is required
md-input-container.md-block(flex)
  label Country
  md-select(
    ng-model='vm.page.contact.Country__c',
    name='contactCountry',
    required,
    ng-disabled='vm.section.errorInitial'
  )
    md-option(ng-repeat='country in vm.page.countries', value='{{ country.Id }}')
      | {{ country.Name }}
  div.hint
    | Which country do you spend the majority of your time in?
  div(ng-messages='vm.form.contactCountry.$error')
    div(ng-message='required')
      | This field is required
